{"tid":1996252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愷樂再失內衣代言 品牌方面揚言未來不會再合作","createTime":"2020-04-30T23:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T12:01:27.000Z","uid":89543,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"670cd7954a00f6b6c8ebcc56b3aea616907e0d8f","tid":1996252,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:16:00.000Z","msg":"台灣歌手羅志祥（小豬）被前度周揚青踢爆私生活淫亂，更與旗下女藝人有長期不正當關係，還點名叫愷樂（蝴蝶姐姐）檢查身體，最後愷樂公開向周揚青道歉，間接承認與小豬偷情。偷情事件令愷樂形象一鋪清袋，繼昨日（27號）有保養品品牌宣佈終止與愷樂的合作後，今日（28號）她再遭代言的內衣品牌「割席」！<br />\n<br />\n據該內衣品牌公關部門人士透露，雙方的合作於去年12月31日結束，而肖像權則到今年6月30日，因為公司政策不再找代言人，故未有與愷樂續約，而未來亦不會再與對方合作。至於風波發生後，確實有消費者因為網站仍有愷樂照片而向品牌查詢，品牌解釋那些只是舊照片，當新貨上架時便會更換愷樂的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBEoiUW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBEoiUW.png&h=960c8a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b12eba69d99253c5a4742fb6e60d01e317aebfaa","tid":1996252,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a10fda92843e530e7edd71dd61081e9270d418ac","tid":1996252,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:31:28.000Z","msg":"做雞啦⋯⋯ 蝴蝶姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb67019d59325e51ab8d92b9b142ef059def45bc","tid":1996252,"uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9vuQloFDqxzJWwZ3mKiCwA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/242fafb760f39bedb091eab4ca097039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9vuQloFDqxzJWwZ3mKiCwA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F242fafb760f39bedb091eab4ca097039&h=74373b8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d2e3fd5fe668486ddc0be6376a8dea793fc2dbb","tid":1996252,"uid":149371,"li